HEADWORD: Chivachie
<hw>Chiv"a*chie`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>chevauchie</ets>, <ets>chevauch⟦eacute⟧e</ets>; of the same origin
as E. <ets>cavalcade</ets>.]</ety> <def>A cavalry raid; hence, a
military expedition.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
